{"tid":1518582,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家明天見到有人在街行, 一齊打電話報警,","createTime":"2019-08-30T09:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T10:36:32.000Z","uid":281875,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"33331d0d2be29cdd209945283766ca4f6ed51632","tid":1518582,"uid":281875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T09:45:07.000Z","msg":"警方指明天以不同理由上街遊行可能違法<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】警方表示留意到有人計劃明天以不同理由上街遊行，例如去銅鑼灣行街、到維園賞花、831自由行，以及宗教遊行等，<strong><ins>指這些行為可能涉嫌非法集結</ins></strong>，警方會適時採取執法行動。<br />\n<br />\n警方又說過去一天，針對過去兩個月來的違法活動再拘捕了七人，分別涉及六月廿一日包圍警察總部、七月一日闖入立法會、七月十三日上水遊行、七月十四日沙田遊行，以及721元朗襲擊事件，重申任何案件不理當事人背景，都會嚴厲跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=361042&amp;fbclid=IwAR1TMgERqMQPhje5rQX1tC5rsMO7RPcUwXK7R9o8ng2x4TCwHvsFRR2889k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361042%26fbclid%3DIwAR1TMgERqMQPhje5rQX1tC5rsMO7RPcUwXK7R9o8ng2x4TCwHvsFRR2889k&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUim58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=005d49be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361042%26fbclid%3DIwAR1TMgERqMQPhje5rQX1tC5rsMO7RPcUwXK7R9o8ng2x4TCwHvsFRR2889k&h=54a6303c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=361042&amp;fbclid=IwAR1TMgERqMQPhje5rQX1tC5rsMO7RPcUwXK7R9o8ng2x4TCwHvsFRR2889k</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家明天見到有人在街行, 一齊打電話報警, <br />\n大家明天見到有人在街行, 一齊打電話報警, <br />\n大家明天見到有人在街行, 一齊打電話報警, <br />\n大家明天見到有人在街行, 一齊打電話報警, <br />\n大家明天見到有人在街行, 一齊打電話報警,"},{"pid":"d1c85f22531dbb706cad03ef1f6fdedbc0f359be","tid":1518582,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T09:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OUQvG7y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOUQvG7y.gif&h=0b84475f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\